00:32:42,561 --> 00:32:44,663
and reinforcement
and repetition.
I know.

546
00:32:44,663 --> 00:32:46,065
That's enough, Andrew.

547
00:32:52,271 --> 00:32:54,303
Well...

548
00:32:54,303 --> 00:32:57,546
At least somebody
is learning something
around here.

549
00:32:57,546 --> 00:32:58,547
What did he say?

550
00:32:58,547 --> 00:33:00,449
Ah.

551
00:33:00,449 --> 00:33:03,412
Your son
doesn't like you
very much, doctor.

552
00:33:03,412 --> 00:33:05,114
Hi, there.

553
00:33:16,725 --> 00:33:18,427
Look, Andrew,

554
00:33:18,427 --> 00:33:21,100
I never planned
