555
00:33:21,100 --> 00:33:23,772
Your mother certainly
never dreamed of it,

556
00:33:23,772 --> 00:33:26,675
but we need
Dr. Prentiss' help now.

557
00:33:29,338 --> 00:33:30,739
Wouldn't it make
jennie's life richer

558
00:33:30,739 --> 00:33:34,113
