If we could speak to her?

559
00:33:34,113 --> 00:33:36,045
That's what Dr. Prentiss
is trying to do.

560
00:33:36,045 --> 00:33:38,587
Jennie's
not an experiment,

561
00:33:38,587 --> 00:33:41,250
and that's all
she is to Dr. Prentiss.

562
00:33:41,250 --> 00:33:46,195
Do you have any idea
the stature Dr. Prentiss has--

563
00:33:46,195 --> 00:33:47,296
