564
00:33:47,296 --> 00:33:51,930
Ph.d at 23.
15 years of fieldwork.

565
00:33:51,930 --> 00:33:54,633
Full scholarship
at Harvard and Cambridge.

566
00:33:54,633 --> 00:33:55,934
Just like you.

567
00:33:55,934 --> 00:33:58,537
What is that
supposed to mean?

568
00:33:58,537 --> 00:34:01,140
Your work is more
important to you

569
00:34:01,140 --> 00:34:02,411
than anything else
in the world,

570
00:34:02,411 --> 00:34:04,413
