[Sighs]

576
00:34:36,445 --> 00:34:37,806
What?

577
00:34:47,356 --> 00:34:50,359
All right now.

578
00:34:52,020 --> 00:34:53,021
Jennie.

579
00:34:53,021 --> 00:34:56,064
You, jennie.

580
00:34:56,064 --> 00:34:58,727
[Cackles]

581
00:34:58,727 --> 00:35:00,899
What is this?

582
00:35:04,573 --> 00:35:07,136
[Jennie screeches]

583
00:35:07,136 --> 00:35:10,479
Ok, ok. Apple.

584
00:35:10,479 --> 00:35:14,012
Pfft.
Apple.

585
00:35:28,096 --> 00:35:32,100
Ok, ok, ok.

586
00:35:32,961 --> 00:35:34,903
Don't you dare.

587
00:35:34,903 --> 00:35:36,805
I'm warning you.

588
00:35:36,805 --> 00:35:39,838
