pleasantly back
all evening.

593
00:35:46,845 --> 00:35:48,917
Do you think
I'm looking forward
to that?

594
00:35:48,917 --> 00:35:51,580
Huh? I think not.

595
00:35:57,155 --> 00:36:00,559
So help me, I will
lock you in the basement.

596
00:36:00,559 --> 00:36:02,791
[Whimpers]

597
00:36:02,791 --> 00:36:04,693
That's better.

598
00:36:14,473 --> 00:36:16,174
[Gasps]

599
00:36:18,947 --> 00:36:21,550
Oh, you horrible
creature.

600
00:36:24,953 --> 00:36:28,217
That's it. I have had it
with you, young lady.

601
00:36:30,459 --> 00:36:32,261
[Screeches]
Oh, you let go,

602
00:36:32,261 --> 00:36:34,623
you miserable
beast.

603
00:36:34,623 --> 00:36:37,796
Ok,
you stay there.

604
00:36:37,796 --> 00:36:40,599
Stay. Stay.

605
00:36:43,732 --> 00:36:45,704
What?

606
00:36:52,811 --> 00:36:54,513
What?

607
00:36:58,116 --> 00:37:00,619
Hug who?

608
00:37:00,619 --> 00:37:04,293
Who are you?

609
00:37:06,695 --> 00:37:09,998
Jennie, that's right.

610
00:37:09,998 --> 00:37:12,531
Come here. Come on.

611
00:37:12,531 --> 00:37:15,464
Oh, good.
Good job.

612
00:37:17,966 --> 00:37:20,068
Wait. Wait.
Wait right here.

613
00:37:21,710 --> 00:37:23,241
Kids. Kids.

614
00:37:23,241 --> 00:37:25,574
You guys,
come down here.
Hurry up.

615
00:37:25,574 --> 00:37:29,518
What?
What is it?

616
00:37:29,518 --> 00:37:30,849
What? What's wrong?

617
00:37:30,849 --> 00:37:33,622
Watch. Watch this.
Watch this.

618
00:37:33,622 --> 00:37:36,385
Jennie. Jennie.

619
00:37:36,385 --> 00:37:38,957
Who is this?

620
00:37:41,159 --> 00:37:43,332
Yes. Yes.

621
00:37:43,332 --> 00:37:44,363
She understands.

622
00:37:44,363 --> 00:37:47,235
Go. Call your father.
He's at the office.

623
00:37:47,235 --> 00:37:50,539
Sarah: Sarah. Sarah.

624
00:38:07,386 --> 00:38:09,788
She spoke!

625
00:38:09,788 --> 00:38:12,020
She spoke!
Whoo-hoo!

626
00:38:12,020 --> 00:38:14,162
Whoo-hoo!

627
00:38:14,162 --> 00:38:16,465
Walter, she spoke.

628
00:38:16,465 --> 00:38:17,826
Who?

629
00:38:17,826 --> 00:38:21,129
Jennie. She understands.

630
00:38:21,129 --> 00:38:23,502
Tremendous.
Have you called Pamela?

631
00:38:23,502 --> 00:38:25,634
Uh, she's on her way
to the house right now.

632
00:38:25,634 --> 00:38:27,806
[Bangs]
Gotta go.

633
00:38:28,807 --> 00:38:30,879
Congratulations.

634
00:38:37,015 --> 00:38:38,687
Andrew: Good job.

635
00:38:38,687 --> 00:38:39,788
♪ You got ♪

