637
00:38:43,892 --> 00:38:45,894
♪ whoa, whoa, yeah ♪

638
00:38:45,894 --> 00:38:49,928
♪ time to live
and time to grow ♪

639
00:38:49,928 --> 00:38:51,760
♪ you know you got ♪

