641
00:38:55,604 --> 00:38:57,506
♪ oh, yeah ♪

642
00:38:57,506 --> 00:39:00,268
♪ I been fighting
night and day ♪

643
00:39:00,268 --> 00:39:03,372
♪ yeah, yeah, yeah ♪

644
00:39:03,372 --> 00:39:06,144
♪ and it's
a mixed up world ♪

645
00:39:06,144 --> 00:39:09,448
♪ but don't hesitate ♪

646
00:39:09,448 --> 00:39:12,851
♪ and waste
your life away ♪

647
00:39:12,851 --> 00:39:13,982
♪ no, because ♪

648
00:39:13,982 --> 00:39:18,727
♪ life is always
