00:39:18,727 --> 00:39:21,660
♪ yes, give it a chance ♪

650
00:39:21,660 --> 00:39:24,292
♪ why not try it today? ♪

651
00:39:24,292 --> 00:39:27,135
♪ So I said, rise up ♪

652
00:39:27,135 --> 00:39:30,569
♪ you know you can rise up ♪
[Doorbell rings]

653
00:39:30,569 --> 00:39:35,474
♪ Oh, whoa,
and take a stand, ah ♪

654
00:39:41,149 --> 00:39:43,782
Well, hello there,
young lady.

655
00:39:43,782 --> 00:39:45,253
[Screeches]

656
00:39:45,253 --> 00:39:46,685
Aah!

657
00:39:46,685 --> 00:39:48,857
[Cries]
Rita.

658
00:39:48,857 --> 00:39:52,360
♪ Don't you know
we can rise up ♪

659
00:39:52,360 --> 00:39:55,794
Bless you. Enjoy.

660
00:39:55,794 --> 00:39:59,428
♪ And take a stand, ah? ♪

661
00:39:59,428 --> 00:40:01,129
♪ Rise up,
rise up, rise up ♪

662
00:40:01,129 --> 00:40:02,571
♪ rise up ♪

