681
00:40:45,744 --> 00:40:47,646
What do you think?

682
00:40:47,646 --> 00:40:48,947
Well...

683
00:40:50,649 --> 00:40:52,020
I think she deserves
the dignity

684
00:40:52,020 --> 00:40:54,653
