of a circus animal.

685
00:40:54,653 --> 00:40:57,726
Come on, jennie.

686
00:40:58,827 --> 00:41:01,790
How dare you talk
to me like that.

687
00:41:01,790 --> 00:41:04,032
This is my house
and jennie is...

688
00:41:04,032 --> 00:41:06,294
Your what,
Mrs. Archibald?

689
00:41:18,707 --> 00:41:21,950
She's reached the age
where she needs to live
in a safe environment.

690
00:41:21,950 --> 00:41:25,183
And that would be
the tahachee center
run by you, of course.

691
00:41:25,183 --> 00:41:27,055
