to jennie.

692
00:41:27,055 --> 00:41:29,918
Hugo, there's no need
for animosity here.

693
00:41:29,918 --> 00:41:32,220
Dr. Prentiss'
concern is genuine.

694
00:41:32,220 --> 00:41:34,462
The situation
is impossible.

695
00:41:34,462 --> 00:41:35,724
Jennie's
being tended to

696
00:41:35,724 --> 00:41:38,066
