as "undisciplined."

699
00:41:41,399 --> 00:41:42,731
We are not experiments.

700
00:41:42,731 --> 00:41:44,673
We're not subjects
in a laboratory.

701
00:41:44,673 --> 00:41:46,635
We are a family.

702
00:41:46,635 --> 00:41:49,037
