at our home.

720
00:42:31,920 --> 00:42:35,083
If this situation
is no longer
suitable for you,

721
00:42:35,083 --> 00:42:36,625
then your project
with her is over.

722
00:42:36,625 --> 00:42:40,328
Thank you, Walter.

723
00:42:50,939 --> 00:42:52,100
Hugo.

724
00:42:54,402 --> 00:42:56,174
