brilliant scientists
I've ever known.

727
00:43:01,880 --> 00:43:03,782
What are you
getting at, Walter?

728
00:43:03,782 --> 00:43:07,155
Usually,
an animal imprints

729
00:43:07,155 --> 00:43:09,217
